### 👥 B. Sales Representative Performance & Target Evaluation
To evaluate efficiency, actual annual revenues were benchmarked against assigned targets. 

> ⚠️ Methodology Note for Technical Recruiters: The raw default dashboard metrics initially displayed a massive, misleading variance (showing representatives exceeding monthly targets by 239% to 754%). This occurred because an *annualized actual sales figure* was being compared directly against a single *monthly target boundary*. 

To fix this metric distortion and provide true corporate accuracy, the analytical logic was adjusted to calculate True Annual Target Attainment:

$$\text{True Target Achievement \%} = \frac{\text{Actual Annual Revenue}}{\text{Monthly Target} \times 12} \times 100$$

